OL,3,CCardiff University staff vote for
OL,4,Cstrike action over proposed job losses
OL,6,FCardiff University staff have voted to
OL,7,Fgo ahead with strike action over
OL,8,Fproposed job cuts at the university.
OL,10,FThe University and Colleges Union
OL,11,F(UCU) says, "83% (of members) backed
OL,12,Fstrike action and 86% backed action
OL,13,Fshort of strike up to and including an
OL,14,Fassessment boycott".
OL,16,FThe action means coursework and exams
OL,17,Fcould go unmarked, and could mean
OL,18,Fdisruption to this summer's
OL,19,Fgraduations.
