OL,3,CCardiff University staff vote for
OL,4,Cstrike action over proposed job losses
OL,6,FThe union balloted staff over
OL,7,Findustrial action after Cardiff
OL,8,FUniversity announced potential cuts,
OL,9,Fincluding up to 400 job losses and
OL,10,Fschool and subject closures.
OL,12,FThe university said that reducing
OL,13,Ftheir academic headcount by compulsory
OL,14,Fredundancy will only happen if it's
OL,15,Fabsolutely necessary. They say the
OL,16,Fchanges are being proposed to "secure
OL,17,Fthe university's long-term future."
