OL,3,CCardiff University staff vote for
OL,4,Cstrike action over proposed job losses
OL,6,FCardiff University's UCU branch
OL,7,Fpresident, Dr Joey Whitfield, said,
OL,8,F"This ballot result shows Cardiff
OL,9,Fstaff are utterly opposed to the cruel
OL,10,Fand unnecessary cuts management are
OL,11,Ftrying to force through.
OL,13,F"It's time for Cardiff University
OL,14,Fleaders to listen to staff, and the
OL,15,Fhuge amount of public, political,
OL,16,Fcultural, and community support we
OL,17,Fhave built, before they further damage
OL,18,Fthe University's tattered reputation.
