OL,3,CCardiff University staff vote for
OL,4,Cstrike action over proposed job losses
OL,6,FA Cardiff University spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is disappointing as
OL,8,Findustrial action will inevitably
OL,9,Fcause disruption for some of our
OL,10,Fstudents. We will do everything we can
OL,11,Fto minimise its impact.
OL,13,F"It is important to stress that this
OL,14,Faction will not impact the whole
OL,15,FUniversity. The university will remain
OL,16,Fopen and in many areas teaching,
OL,17,Fresearch and services will be
OL,18,Funaffected. We recognise that these
OL,19,Fare extremely difficult and
OL,20,Fchallenging times.
